Gedit macropy
==============

This is a plugin for [Gedit][2] 3, the official text editor of the GNOME 
desktop environment. This plugin is for Gedit versions 3 and above.
 **This plugin is NOT compatible with Gedit 2.x**.

Macropy adds some menu options and buttons to the menu-bar to record and 
playback macros with Gedit.

Installation
------------

1. Download the source code from this repository.
2. Copy the files to the Gedit plugins directory 
'~/.local/share/gedit/plugins/'.
3. Restart Gedit and enable the plugin.
    
[1]: http://www.gedit.org



